        "rtf_CVd8LC": {
          "type": "rtf",
          "settings": {
            "richtext_content": "<h1></h1><h3>FAQ's</h3><p><strong>Q: Where can I park?</strong><br/>A: Free parking - Denton Working Men's Club & Institute, 3 Fredrick St, Denton, Manchester, M34 3JB.<br/><a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/dir/?api=1&destination=Denton+Working+Men%27s+Club+%26+Institute%2C+3+Fredrick+St%2C+Denton%2C+Manchester%2C+M34+3JB\" target=\"_blank\">Get Directions</a></p><p><strong>Q: How does the points system work?</strong><br/>A: Each discipline contributes points towards the 1,000-point threshold. E.g. 150KG deadlift = 150 points, 100 cals = 100 points.</p><p><strong>Q: Do I need prior experience?</strong><br/>A: Having a good level of fitness is advised, however the Games are designed for athletes of all levels; staff will guide you safely through each challenge.</p><p><strong>Q: Can I attend just to watch?</strong><br/>A: Absolutely. Tickets are required for participation; spectators are welcome to attend.</p><p><strong>Q: How do I redeem my voucher code for Gym King?</strong><br/>A: Your unique code will be included with your ticket confirmation.</p><h3>Safety</h3><p>All participants must complete a waiver prior to entry. Safety and wellbeing are our priorities, and signing the waiver is required for participation in any physical activities.</p>"
          }
        }
